{
  "texts": [
    "The potential of color images, such as RGB images, in evaluating the quality of agricultural products is limited by their narrow range of band information.",
    "Hence, HSI reconstruction represents a notable advancement in the field of agricultural and food sciences.",
    "This specialized branch of HSI technology is dedicated to creating high-quality spectral images, providing a more in-depth analysis of critical quality parameters such as moisture content, nutrient levels, defects and the presence of contaminants in agri-food products.",
    "These insights are crucial for ensuring the safety and overall quality of food.",
    "Notably, HSI reconstruction offers a more resource-efficient approach compared to traditional HSI methods, proving particularly beneficial for the agricultural commodities grading industry."
  ]
}